Tavatron watched Dinobot out of the corner of her eye as the computer 
completed its scan:

*One new signature. Faction unknown.* Tavatron sighed, that was just great. 
The last thing they needed were more enemies. Tavatron watched Dinobot as he 
prepared to leave the ship. She silently walked up behind him:

"Liono said to stay at base." Tavatron transformed (to B.M.) and sat beside 
Dinobot. She was still concerned about him. Dinobot's hate for his enemies 
could cloud his judgement. Clouded judgement before and/or during battle 
could be a costly mistake.
